  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/65100d83c9c9f2e38eab50251c754c2e.poster.avif?t=1772888302\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/65100d83c9c9f2e38eab50251c754c2e.webm?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/65100d83c9c9f2e38eab50251c754c2e.mp4?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS: The game was developed by one person.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dark PGT – A Souls-like Comedy Mini-Game on Unreal Engine 5</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mad Journey: A Ticket to the Unknown</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far are you willing to go? And is there a way back?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path, make insane decisions, and try not to lose your mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take on the role of a military alcoholic with a mysterious gift—or perhaps a curse—seeing glimpses of the future… or just suffering from hallucinations. Travel to USSR village in the year 2030 to uncover its dark secrets and lift the curse haunting this strange settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a nightmarish future and try to understand: what is really happening here? How did the world descend into this madness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll face hordes of mutated inhabitants—madmen, street prophets, and mysterious mutant grannies unleashing chaos from their balconies. Survive, fight, tear through enemies, and carve your way to the truth. Is this reality, or just the product of a delusional mind?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or are you ready to live your entire life in a place where every day is Groundhog Day?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take on one of the toughest games on the planet without losing your sanity?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are giving you one of the rarest gifts that no one else will ever give you – the experience of completing Dark PGT.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/79a3b42fa1b91735e3b6facf77ae474d.poster.avif?t=1772888302\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/79a3b42fa1b91735e3b6facf77ae474d.webm?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/79a3b42fa1b91735e3b6facf77ae474d.mp4?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal game world— The enemy is ruthless, tearing through everything to destroy you. Your end is near.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extreme difficulty—worthy of a Souls-like game. But much worse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No character progression—you, your sword, and your combat experience in similar games are all that matter on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/6e7d3cb01b5402e21d93448716ec405f.poster.avif?t=1772888302\" width=800 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/6e7d3cb01b5402e21d93448716ec405f.webm?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/6e7d3cb01b5402e21d93448716ec405f.mp4?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/65100d83c9c9f2e38eab50251c754c2e.poster.avif?t=1772888302\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/65100d83c9c9f2e38eab50251c754c2e.webm?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/65100d83c9c9f2e38eab50251c754c2e.mp4?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS: The game was developed by one person.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dark PGT – A Souls-like Comedy Mini-Game on Unreal Engine 5</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mad Journey: A Ticket to the Unknown</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far are you willing to go? And is there a way back?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path, make insane decisions, and try not to lose your mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take on the role of a military alcoholic with a mysterious gift—or perhaps a curse—seeing glimpses of the future… or just suffering from hallucinations. Travel to USSR village in the year 2030 to uncover its dark secrets and lift the curse haunting this strange settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a nightmarish future and try to understand: what is really happening here? How did the world descend into this madness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll face hordes of mutated inhabitants—madmen, street prophets, and mysterious mutant grannies unleashing chaos from their balconies. Survive, fight, tear through enemies, and carve your way to the truth. Is this reality, or just the product of a delusional mind?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or are you ready to live your entire life in a place where every day is Groundhog Day?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take on one of the toughest games on the planet without losing your sanity?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are giving you one of the rarest gifts that no one else will ever give you – the experience of completing Dark PGT.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/79a3b42fa1b91735e3b6facf77ae474d.poster.avif?t=1772888302\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/79a3b42fa1b91735e3b6facf77ae474d.webm?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/79a3b42fa1b91735e3b6facf77ae474d.mp4?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal game world— The enemy is ruthless, tearing through everything to destroy you. Your end is near.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extreme difficulty—worthy of a Souls-like game. But much worse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No character progression—you, your sword, and your combat experience in similar games are all that matter on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/6e7d3cb01b5402e21d93448716ec405f.poster.avif?t=1772888302\" width=800 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/6e7d3cb01b5402e21d93448716ec405f.webm?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3379650/extras/6e7d3cb01b5402e21d93448716ec405f.mp4?t=1772888302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
